data.eml:eml: A taxonomic study of Chinese Empoascini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Typhlocybinae) (III)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Qin, Dao-Zheng, Liu, Yang, Zhang, Ya-Lin (2011): A taxonomic study of Chinese Empoascini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Typhlocybinae) (III). Zootaxa 3094: 30-42, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.203357
